Package: DataEntry
Version: 2026.0.0.3
Author: Mihai Valcu
Maintainer: Mihai Valcu <Mihai.Valcu@bi.mpg.de>
Title: Shiny Data Entry Interfaces for Database Tables
Description: Build Shiny applications for entering and editing database tables with rhandsontable. Provides table-specific validation, editable validation rules, database save workflows, and backup support for MariaDB-backed data entry.
